{"tid":2464163,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU受訪把「台灣和中國」並列國家　小粉紅氣炸：脫粉了","createTime":"2021-03-27T09:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T09:43:40.000Z","uid":16659,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c7f1e7feaa0beb53576cdeaa30246d47a73aafde","tid":2464163,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:02:54.000Z","msg":"韓國女星IU李知恩睽違四年推出了第五張專輯《LILAC》，在MV預告中一口氣狂換了7種造型，讓粉絲們嗨翻，沒想到卻有中國網友翻出她過去的訪談，在提及世界「各國」的粉絲時，把印度、中國、台灣、日本並列國家，讓小粉紅們氣炸直呼「有夠無語」、「就這樣吧，脫粉了」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/03/03/2436619-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F03%2F03%2F2436619-PH.jpg&h=12abd816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU過去的訪談被挖出來，引發中國網友撻伐。（圖／翻攝自當事人IG）<br />\n<br />\n或許是人紅是非多，IU李知恩過去的採訪又被人重新挖出來，掀起中國愛國網友們的撻伐。IU在直播中表示「世界各國的粉絲們，大家都在看嗎？對了，聽說這個是全球頻道，印度、中國、台灣、日本等等，如果我能用各國語言跟大家打招呼就好了」，因為將中國和台灣並列國家，引發砲轟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/27/3084708-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F27%2F3084708-PH.jpg&h=7f369ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU受訪時把台灣和中國、日本、印度並列。（圖／翻攝自頭號明星微博）<br />\n<br />\n事後有中國粉絲澄清，這是翻譯的問題，IU受訪時提到台灣是用了「各地」，也就是地區的意思，並表示是遭到黑粉們斷章取義，但許多小粉紅們並不接受這種說詞，痛批把台灣並列在中國和日本中間也很怪，「太無語了」、「粉絲洗什麼白呢？這些問題上難道不是以國家為先」、「這人沒文化唄，才會把台灣跟國家並列」、「不管有沒有地區兩個字，把台灣和其他國家放在一起，不是問題嗎」、「到底誰會這樣說」、「有夠無力的澄清」。<br />\n<br />\n不少台灣網友看了則笑翻，「笑中國人不敢拒聽IU的歌」、「我才覺得跟中國擺在一起無語勒」、「小粉紅最近很忙啊」、「小粉紅真的很閒」、「這已經是幾年前的採訪了吧，有沒有那麼閒還翻出來罵」。"},{"pid":"db78aed0bd031c63eab88b2417ce46cf182c51ae","tid":2464163,"uid":125168,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842681535aed0e944ce085c7580afb8b4b2b1e50","tid":2464163,"uid":478,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"db78aed0bd031c63eab88b2417ce46cf182c51ae","tid":2464163,"uid":125168,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:07:20.000Z","msg":"支那肯研發氣炸鍋<br />\n會唔會技術領先全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7a6633b3c184b1b6dd4f72ed7f761acd58e2e3","tid":2464163,"uid":93096,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"db78aed0bd031c63eab88b2417ce46cf182c51ae","tid":2464163,"uid":125168,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:07:35.000Z","msg":"氣炸師...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fda65843c87dce6ec273cc3edfc5cdba174099","tid":2464163,"uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:09:13.000Z","msg":"上次孝利單野,即時一堆帳號拎舒華出黎笑佢肥<br />\n今次又咁啱啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5504e5efa83b77ebba038ea8400833a98daffb47","tid":2464163,"uid":16365,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:11:55.000Z","msg":"我IU世界第一！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ee2b52c8c5e3d7ace71963bce8e9c52e8feacf","tid":2464163,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:12:29.000Z","msg":"手足IU<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27e1f3b51e0f6870a8dc94de28afe9bf7e91c39","tid":2464163,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5504e5efa83b77ebba038ea8400833a98daffb47","tid":2464163,"uid":16365,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:11:55.000Z","msg":"我IU世界第一！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"IU=手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d860060a6b4065860fe1b11193168b168dbdc3","tid":2464163,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"咁佢係唔啱嘅，係人都知台灣係中國嘅一部份"},{"pid":"2ab9f2a8b713694a8f1c2c1c2a1e48e68de02ee0","tid":2464163,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:17:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁佢係唔啱嘅，係人都知台灣係中國嘅一部份</blockquote><br />\nYES 全世界都係中國一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69c369cfd18ebe19bd7bd93d3035fe974034aad","tid":2464163,"uid":362366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:19:17.000Z","msg":"氣炸什麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣國語的確有別於中國普通話<br />\n中華民國亦比中華人民共和國有更遠久的歷史"},{"pid":"f5ba7eff345cc2bc736a45fb67a25329e2b44a43","tid":2464163,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f69c369cfd18ebe19bd7bd93d3035fe974034aad","tid":2464163,"uid":362366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:19:17.000Z","msg":"氣炸什麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣國語的確有別於中國普通話<br />\n中華民國亦比中華人民共和國有更遠久的歷史"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:21:43.000Z","msg":"全世界都係中華人民共和國一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4361410a4afe47fc566059f422416f51574edaf3","tid":2464163,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34ee2b52c8c5e3d7ace71963bce8e9c52e8feacf","tid":2464163,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:12:29.000Z","msg":"手足IU<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:26:37.000Z","msg":"IU好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1876c354b32851395a7e47b4a70e479be28a58","tid":2464163,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4361410a4afe47fc566059f422416f51574edaf3","tid":2464163,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34ee2b52c8c5e3d7ace71963bce8e9c52e8fe